         <abstract>
            <p>Let f(x) be a monic polynomial in Z[x]. We observe a statistical relation of roots of f(x) in different local fields
              $Q_p $
              , where f(x) decomposes completely. Based on this, we propose several conjectures.</p>
         </abstract>
